function info($str) { echo "INFO: $str\n"; }
function warn($str) { echo "WARNING: $str\n"; }
function err($str) { die("FATAL ERROR: $str\n"); }

@set_time_limit(0);

@header('Content-Type: text/plain');

chdir(__DIR__);
if (trim(@file_get_contents('.version.php')) !== '<?php // Revision 1115') {
	err('This update can only be applied to OIDplus version 2.0.0.1115!');
}

if (version_compare(PHP_VERSION, '7.0.0') < 0) {
	err('You need PHP Version 7.0 to update to this version');
}

// Dir added: .idea
@mkdir('.idea');
if (!is_dir('.idea')) {
	warn('Directory could not be created: .idea');
} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('.idea', 0755)) {
	warn('Could not change directory permissions of .idea');
}

// File added: .idea/.gitignore
function writefile_1() {
	@$fp = fopen('.idea/.gitignore', 'w');
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('IyBEZWZhdWx0IGlnbm9yZWQgZmlsZXMNCi9zaGVsZi8NCi93b3Jrc3BhY2UueG1sDQojIEVkaXRvci1iYXNlZCBIVFRQIENsaWVudCByZXF1ZXN0cw0KL2h0dHBSZXF1ZXN0cy8NCiMgRGF0YXNvdXJjZSBsb2NhbCBzdG9yYWdlIGlnbm9yZWQgZmlsZXMNCi9kYXRh'));
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('U291cmNlcy8NCi9kYXRhU291cmNlcy5sb2NhbC54bWwNCg=='));
	@fclose($fp);
}
if (is_file('.idea/.gitignore') && (sha1_file('.idea/.gitignore') != '2e8e3f2c21083bfc1741db5df016b198b53ae6ad')) {
	warn('File was created by someone else. Will overwrite the changes now: .idea/.gitignore');
	$tmp = pathinfo('.idea/.gitignore');
	$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('.idea/.gitignore')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
	warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
	if (!@copy('.idea/.gitignore', $backup_name)) {
		warn('Creation of backup failed');
	}
}
writefile_1();
if (!is_file('.idea/.gitignore')) {
	warn('File cannot be created (not existing): .idea/.gitignore');
} else if (sha1_file('.idea/.gitignore') != '2e8e3f2c21083bfc1741db5df016b198b53ae6ad') {
	warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): .idea/.gitignore');
} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('.idea/.gitignore', 0644)) {
	warn('Could not change file permissions of .idea/.gitignore');
}

if (!is_file('ajax.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: ajax.php');
	writefile_10();
	if (!is_file('ajax.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): ajax.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('ajax.php') != '0bc5715fba83d501c62604b854a66c32440c45a8') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): ajax.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('ajax.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of ajax.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('ajax.php') !== '0bc5715fba83d501c62604b854a66c32440c45a8') {
		if (@sha1_file('ajax.php') !== 'c05bc188215142f9253ada89ffb37dbfdc604217') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: ajax.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('ajax.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('ajax.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('ajax.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_10();
		if (@sha1_file('ajax.php') !== '0bc5715fba83d501c62604b854a66c32440c45a8') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): ajax.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('composer.json')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: composer.json');
	writefile_11();
	if (!is_file('composer.json')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): composer.json');
	} else if (sha1_file('composer.json') != '8265e1b912b73be03356750aaccd7a01c05f0a46') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): composer.json');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('composer.json', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of composer.json');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('composer.json') !== '8265e1b912b73be03356750aaccd7a01c05f0a46') {
		if (@sha1_file('composer.json') !== 'fb0a919999549b1bb1a62087a5d63d8b57640797') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: composer.json');
			$tmp = pathinfo('composer.json');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('composer.json')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('composer.json', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_11();
		if (@sha1_file('composer.json') !== '8265e1b912b73be03356750aaccd7a01c05f0a46') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): composer.json');
		}
	}
}

			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/systemid_collider');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/systemid_collider')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/systemid_collider', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_15();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/systemid_collider') !== '2436c519e6db0ef064eb12a0bb86791364238e8e') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/systemid_collider');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps');
	writefile_16();
	if (!is_file('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps') != 'fdd2e9e2689ed22f32786fde56b6c6bf1123979b') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps') !== 'fdd2e9e2689ed22f32786fde56b6c6bf1123979b') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps') !== 'd9845aa05bc21ee0d1eeb76075e0511869accad8') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_16();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps') !== 'fdd2e9e2689ed22f32786fde56b6c6bf1123979b') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('dev/translation/show_nontranslated_code.phps')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/translation/show_nontranslated_code.phps');
	writefile_17();
	if (!is_file('dev/translation/show_nontranslated_code.phps')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/translation/show_nontranslated_code.phps');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/translation/show_nontranslated_code.phps') != 'a49319dc3d701166edd44f5db207a71ad4e6f616') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/translation/show_nontranslated_code.phps');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/translation/show_nontranslated_code.phps', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/translation/show_nontranslated_code.phps');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/translation/show_nontranslated_code.phps') !== 'a49319dc3d701166edd44f5db207a71ad4e6f616') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/translation/show_nontranslated_code.phps') !== 'bf6b2e5210b20b0742729610dce85271563271a7') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/translation/show_nontranslated_code.phps');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/translation/show_nontranslated_code.phps');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/translation/show_nontranslated_code.phps')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/translation/show_nontranslated_code.phps', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_17();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/translation/show_nontranslated_code.phps') !== 'a49319dc3d701166edd44f5db207a71ad4e6f616') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/translation/show_nontranslated_code.phps');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php');
	writefile_29();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php') != 'de79a28f0df00e98db6f72545c5759ade74fe3cd') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php') !== 'de79a28f0df00e98db6f72545c5759ade74fe3cd') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php') !== 'dbb1a8c5d3c45de5a28ff378462eded93917f0e3') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_29();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php') !== 'de79a28f0df00e98db6f72545c5759ade74fe3cd') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplusCookieUtils.class.php');
	writefile_30();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusCookieUtils.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusCookieUtils.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusCookieUtils.class.php') != 'd616444a11cd58722badcbd6891ff62ee6bdaebb') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusCookieUtils.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusCookieUtils.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusCookieUtils.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusCookieUtils.class.php') !== 'd616444a11cd58722badcbd6891ff62ee6bdaebb') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusCookieUtils.class.php') !== '64b601bc5fb749faac382ace6bcd2c4056ca84ae') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusCookieUtils.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplusCookieUtils.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplusCookieUtils.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusCookieUtils.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_30();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusCookieUtils.class.php') !== 'd616444a11cd58722badcbd6891ff62ee6bdaebb') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusCookieUtils.class.php');
		}
	}
}

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php') != '82e7737afe626b6c923ca724e92c34d01f1fee5f') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php');

	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php') !== '82e7737afe626b6c923ca724e92c34d01f1fee5f') {

			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php', $backup_name)) {

			}
		}
		writefile_31();

			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusLogger.class.php', $backup_name)) {

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplusLoggerPlugin.class.php');
	writefile_38();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusLoggerPlugin.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusLoggerPlugin.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusLoggerPlugin.class.php') != '5a0eeaddd48c14c7bd2a65ac73ad79d33d5f401c') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusLoggerPlugin.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusLoggerPlugin.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusLoggerPlugin.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusLoggerPlugin.class.php') !== '5a0eeaddd48c14c7bd2a65ac73ad79d33d5f401c') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusLoggerPlugin.class.php') !== '0ad9e95b78aa30997676990d04157e8fab0459ac') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusLoggerPlugin.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplusLoggerPlugin.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplusLoggerPlugin.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusLoggerPlugin.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_38();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusLoggerPlugin.class.php') !== '5a0eeaddd48c14c7bd2a65ac73ad79d33d5f401c') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusLoggerPlugin.class.php');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplusSQLException.class.php');
	writefile_50();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusSQLException.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusSQLException.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusSQLException.class.php') != '916da9c332e4efa9baf81592b6f9b7b5f3b19255') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusSQLException.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusSQLException.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusSQLException.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusSQLException.class.php') !== '916da9c332e4efa9baf81592b6f9b7b5f3b19255') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusSQLException.class.php') !== 'b856cb65f43fe664837470453344f2ddaa339ca2') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusSQLException.class.php');

			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusSQLException.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_50();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusSQLException.class.php') !== '916da9c332e4efa9baf81592b6f9b7b5f3b19255') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusSQLException.class.php');

	writefile_53();

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/db_updates/update1002.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/db_updates/update1002.inc.php') != '089f4f8e8fc3de64c1d0d41304c277ea8467544c') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/db_updates/update1002.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/db_updates/update1002.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/db_updates/update1002.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/db_updates/update1002.inc.php') !== '089f4f8e8fc3de64c1d0d41304c277ea8467544c') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/db_updates/update1002.inc.php') !== '0812eb99c4182ed1fde7b526b2a5e031e222e24c') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/db_updates/update1002.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/db_updates/update1002.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/db_updates/update1002.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/db_updates/update1002.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_53();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/db_updates/update1002.inc.php') !== '089f4f8e8fc3de64c1d0d41304c277ea8467544c') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/db_updates/update1002.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/functions.inc.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/functions.inc.php');
	writefile_54();
	if (!is_file('includes/functions.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/functions.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/functions.inc.php') != '98ba2c6db31efbe31b5930425bce804a7c140e15') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/functions.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/functions.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/functions.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/functions.inc.php') !== '98ba2c6db31efbe31b5930425bce804a7c140e15') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/functions.inc.php') !== '8dd919c29ef22105ddb835e4763edbf768d59cdd') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/functions.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/functions.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/functions.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/functions.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_54();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/functions.inc.php') !== '98ba2c6db31efbe31b5930425bce804a7c140e15') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/functions.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/oidplus.inc.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/oidplus.inc.php');
	writefile_55();
	if (!is_file('includes/oidplus.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/oidplus.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/oidplus.inc.php') != '6fbc53c8f009a632e5609055ca7e63497b98b40a') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/oidplus.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/oidplus.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/oidplus.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/oidplus.inc.php') !== '6fbc53c8f009a632e5609055ca7e63497b98b40a') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/oidplus.inc.php') !== '5b33eff9ea7059df89a455b1a4e892007e36c887') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/oidplus.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/oidplus.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/oidplus.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/oidplus.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_55();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/oidplus.inc.php') !== '6fbc53c8f009a632e5609055ca7e63497b98b40a') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/oidplus.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('index.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: index.php');
	writefile_58();
	if (!is_file('index.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): index.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('index.php') != '3bb49d86b59bc7f04567616e1fe3ed4a4cbb6c12') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): index.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('index.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of index.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('index.php') !== '3bb49d86b59bc7f04567616e1fe3ed4a4cbb6c12') {
		if (@sha1_file('index.php') !== '638c848a373bbe9052396520a5d1ee86347ea6eb') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: index.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('index.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('index.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('index.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_58();
		if (@sha1_file('index.php') !== '3bb49d86b59bc7f04567616e1fe3ed4a4cbb6c12') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): index.php');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/manifest_plugin_sqlSlang.xsd');
	writefile_72();
	if (!is_file('plugins/manifest_plugin_sqlSlang.xsd')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/manifest_plugin_sqlSlang.xsd');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/manifest_plugin_sqlSlang.xsd') != '341e8df7a32da219282563ed1ac25236419fb4f8') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/manifest_plugin_sqlSlang.xsd');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/manifest_plugin_sqlSlang.xsd', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/manifest_plugin_sqlSlang.xsd');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/manifest_plugin_sqlSlang.xsd') !== '341e8df7a32da219282563ed1ac25236419fb4f8') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/manifest_plugin_sqlSlang.xsd') !== '5a51c73553d464db13abed4d0b5ed16c1e9331a1') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/manifest_plugin_sqlSlang.xsd');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/manifest_plugin_sqlSlang.xsd');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/manifest_plugin_sqlSlang.xsd')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/manifest_plugin_sqlSlang.xsd', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_72();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/manifest_plugin_sqlSlang.xsd') !== '341e8df7a32da219282563ed1ac25236419fb4f8') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/manifest_plugin_sqlSlang.xsd');
		}
	}
}

		if (@sha1_file('plugins/tushevorg/publicPages/2000_uitweaks/OIDplusPagePublicUITweaks.class.php') !== '4bdcf3c330907f26faa6216c49a6ce6327bf727a') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/tushevorg/publicPages/2000_uitweaks/OIDplusPagePublicUITweaks.class.php');
		}
	}
}

		}

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/901_vnag_version_check/vnag.php');

if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	writefile_124();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') != 'a9cc981e1c42c62188a47fc8fde80ff0cf403f9e') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== 'a9cc981e1c42c62188a47fc8fde80ff0cf403f9e') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== '6aeac3de00ab80ec3fd2cd8a0e3c55e4eaddd296') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_124();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== 'a9cc981e1c42c62188a47fc8fde80ff0cf403f9e') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusObjectTypePluginDoi.class.php');
	writefile_132();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusObjectTypePluginDoi.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusObjectTypePluginDoi.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusObjectTypePluginDoi.class.php') != 'a81f91cb627e4d90cd7ffc859a7a87f4b57919c2') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusObjectTypePluginDoi.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusObjectTypePluginDoi.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusObjectTypePluginDoi.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusObjectTypePluginDoi.class.php') !== 'a81f91cb627e4d90cd7ffc859a7a87f4b57919c2') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusObjectTypePluginDoi.class.php') !== 'e20a376e2872e95b4e006167142ca03ca92aba3f') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusObjectTypePluginDoi.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusObjectTypePluginDoi.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusObjectTypePluginDoi.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');

			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusObjectTypePluginDoi.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_132();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusObjectTypePluginDoi.class.php') !== 'a81f91cb627e4d90cd7ffc859a7a87f4b57919c2') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusObjectTypePluginDoi.class.php');
